A) flash the firmware with a CLOSED kernel {see flashing/instructions}

B) enable dev mode to get a terminal:
Settings -> Security {???} -> Dev Mode
phone will restart after it is done installing
you can just wait {about 2 minutes} once it prompts for:
  ~2.6MB additional installation required

C) open a terminal
devel-su #password is rootme
passwd user #any password

D) insert usb, select: sync and connect

1) ssh-config
2) set-host
3) keygen.pl
4) remove-disclaimer
5) FLASH AN OPENMODE KERNEL
###switch to wifi now###
